\title{Extended Implied Weighting Command}
\description{
An \link[R6:R6Class]{R6} class that configures extended implied weighting in
\pkg{nitro}.

Extended implied weighting assigns each character an independent
concavity constant based on its observed homoplasy, rather than using a
single global constant \emph{k}. This wraps the TNT \code{xpiwe} command.
}
